      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.TIwFJCueTgMJBeNz]{Rebound}</p>\n<p>You and all allies within 30 feet gain hardness equal to your Constitution modifier for 1 round. During this time, you can strike your allies with your entropic strike without making an attack roll, and your entropic strike doesn’t deal damage to your allies but instead restores an equivalent number of Hit Points. An ally can’t regain Hit Points from your entropic strike more than once per hour.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Improved</em></strong>: You can make one attack with your entropic strike against an ally when you use your aspect catalyst.</p>"
